values:
Somebody's gonna celebrate his birthday soon! :D

<s>I hope they remember D:</s>

The new single is out~ And I look hot!

My leg hurts a bit though.  I heard chicken soup is good for people who hurt their legs~ no one seems to know how to make it though

The retard Jungmin says Kyujong is pregnant.  Well, he's been showing signs that he is, like morning sickness and cravings.  And then... Youngsaeng someone else too. 

I don't want to deal with this.

...

The house smells like chocolate.  The scent is relaxing.

I'll get more sleep.

Baby seems to be a bit down D:

Don't worry, I love you I'm here for you.  : )

...I've been feeling weird lately...

...it's really weird...

...I've been thinking of this person quite often lately...

...I don't really know if I like that person or not...

...but I'm confused as hell...

...It's a good thing I have an emergency vodka stash.

Life is good.  Yeah.

Baby gave me a Gameboy...

O__O 

I LOVE IT!

I'm so addicted to this Tetris game. Ha.  Mariokart sucks after he kicked my ass on it

I heard Baby had his sex toys shipped over to his mom's house.  Hahahhaha.  I wish I was there to see the woman's expression.  

Don't worry Baby, I support you all the way.

*dies laughing*

Marumir kissed me today.

I knew it.  He really wanted me.  Lovely, hot me.

*pouts*  I know it's your lifetime dream to kiss everyone, but please.  You're Baby's baby brother.  *sigh* This isn't meant to be, Maru. I'm sorry.

XDDDDDD

Hi!  The other guys are on lj already and of course Leader won't be left behind.

Drink, anyone?  Hehe ^o^
